snippet.title: Talisman: Origins English Trailer
snippet.description:
Talisman: Origins is a story-focused single-player game based on the Talisman 4th Revised Edition rules. 

The land of Talisman is home to many wondrous stories and Talisman: Origins lets you play through those fantastic tales and affect their outcomes. 

Available soon on Steam, Google Play Store and the App Store.
